data.description: Seller offering $8,000 towards buyers closing costs/rate buy down. Better than new 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath, 2 car garage fenced home on a large corner lot. A light, bright and airy atmosphere offering the features of a new home without the wait. This home features recessed lighting, wood plank flooring in the main living area, open floor plan, ceiling fans, blinds, a keydrop/organization station complimented with tasteful neutral colors. The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, upgraded cabinets with crown molding, pendant lighting over the eating space at the island, granite countertops and a large walk-in pantry. The master suite includes dual sink vanities with granite countertops, an oversized walk in shower and a large walk in closet. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle from the covered patio overlooking a large backyard on a corner lot, all fenced with gates.
